### **💾 Automated Backup Script (Enhanced)**

#### **ops/backup/automated-backup.sh**
```bash
#!/bin/bash
set -euo pipefail

BACKUP_DIR="/opt/backups/ausclean"
RETENTION_DAYS=30
TIMESTAMP=$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)
BACKUP_FILE="$BACKUP_DIR/ausclean-full-$TIMESTAMP.tar.gz"

echo "💾 Starting full backup..."

mkdir -p "$BACKUP_DIR"

# Database backup
echo "📊 Backing up database..."
docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml exec -T postgres pg_dump -U ausclean_admin ausclean | gzip > "$BACKUP_DIR/ausclean-db-$TIMESTAMP.sql.gz"

# Redis backup (RDB snapshot)
echo "🔴 Backing up Redis..."
docker compose -f docker-compose.prod.yml exec redis redis-cli -a "$REDIS_PASSWORD" BGSAVE
sleep 5
docker cp ausclean-pro-redis-1:/data/dump.rdb "$BACKUP_DIR/redis-dump-$TIMESTAMP.rdb"

# Environment (encrypted)
echo "🔐 Backing up environment..."
tar -czf "$BACKUP_DIR/env-$TIMESTAMP.tar.gz" .env.production

# Full backup archive
echo "📦 Creating full backup archive..."
tar -czf "$BACKUP_FILE" \
    "$BACKUP_DIR/ausclean-db-$TIMESTAMP.sql.gz" \
    "$BACKUP_DIR/redis-dump-$TIMESTAMP.rdb" \
    "$BACKUP_DIR/env-$TIMESTAMP.tar.gz"

# Upload to S3 (or compatible)
echo "☁️  Uploading to S3..."
aws s3 cp "$BACKUP_FILE" "s3://ausclean-backups/$BACKUP_FILE" \
    --sse AES256 \
    --storage-class STANDARD_IA

# Cleanup local old backups
echo "🧹 Cleaning up old backups..."
find "$BACKUP_DIR" -name "*.tar.gz" -mtime +$RETENTION_DAYS -delete
find "$BACKUP_DIR" -name "*.sql.gz" -mtime +$RETENTION_DAYS -delete

# Verify backup integrity
echo "✅ Verifying backup..."
aws s3 ls "s3://ausclean-backups/$BACKUP_FILE"

echo "✅ Backup complete: $BACKUP_FILE"
echo "📊 Size: $(du -h "$BACKUP_FILE" | cut -f1)"

# Send notification (Slack/Email)
curl -X POST -H 'Content-type: application/json' \
    --data "{\"text\":\"✅ Backup completed: $BACKUP_FILE\"}" \
    "$SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL"
```

