| CPU Usage | >70% | >90% | Scale up/out |
| Memory Usage | >80% | >95% | Scale up |
| Request Latency (P95) | >1s | >3s | Scale backend |
| Database Connections | >60% | >85% | Add pooler (PgBouncer) |
| Disk Usage | >70% | >90% | Expand volume |
| Error Rate | >1% | >5% | Investigate + scale |

